schemacrawler.schemacrawler

Class SchemaRetrievalOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • schemacrawler.schemacrawler.SchemaRetrievalOptions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Options

    public final class SchemaRetrievalOptions
extends Object
implements Options
    Provides for database specific overrides for SchemaCrawler functionality. This can add or inject database plugins, or override defaults. It is recommended to build these options using factory methods in SchemaCrawlerUtility.
